{"type": "article", "id": 28219, "title": "海洋塑料制成的太阳眼镜", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-15T06:30:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 32, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702130712ZNQkpWJr9sj1HXhl.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>眼镜品牌 <a href=\"http://www.nortonpoint.com/\">Norton Point</a> 在前不久的世界海洋日推出了一款变废为宝的产品，用回收来的海洋塑料制作而成的 Sea Plastic Differently 太阳眼镜。这些塑料垃圾来自海地，由 Norton Point 的合作伙伴 The Plastic Bank 收集，随后进行处理加工，每一副眼镜都代表着约 453 克的海洋塑料以这种方式重生。如果你对这个项目感兴趣的话可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/nortonpoint/sea-plastic-differently-recycled-ocean-plastic-sun\">链接</a>参与众筹，售价为 99 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130710Aye9Nx4IMF80amiU.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.37260677\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130711PSrFYjZq8ce6Whbs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72205882\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130711l5YenMuXUSdLokCt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.51911765\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}